channel.title: Public Class Duplicate Error? But,theres Only One!(Server GE)
channel.description:
[code].\Server\Player\Client.java:7589: illegal start of expression public int gewaitTimer = 0, checkgewaittimer = 10; ^ .\Server\GrandExchange.java:13: duplicate class: GrandExchange public class GrandExchange ^ .\Server\Player\Client.java:25: cannot access Server.GrandExchange bad class file: .\Server\GrandExchange.java file does not contain class Server.GrandExchange Please remove or make sure it appears in the correct subdirectory of the classpa th. GrandExchange ge = new GrandExchange(); ^ Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
It can't find the File and it seems to think that the Public class GrandExchange has be shown more than once... This always happens to me when I add a new Java file and try to do something like this! Can anyone help me fix this?
Thanks ~Code God Of Rs~ [u][b] What I'm trying to add: http://silabsoft.org/smf/index.php?showtopic=13704[/b][/u]
